## hh_viewer_fastapi


### Creating a virtual environment:

    python -m venv .venv

### Windows: 

    powershell:
    Set-ExecutionPolicy -ExecutionPolicy RemoteSigned -Scope Process

    acivate venv:
    .venv\Scripts\activate

### Install packages:
    pip install -r requirements.txt

### Creating .env file:

    DB_HOST = 'localhost'
    DB_PORT = '5432'
    DB_NAME = 'db_name'
    DB_USER = 'user_name'
    DB_PASSWORD = 'password'

    ADMIN_USER_MODEL=User
    ADMIN_USER_MODEL_USERNAME_FIELD=username
    ADMIN_SECRET_KEY=secret_key

### Preparing migrations:
    aerich init-db
    aerich migrate --name name_migrate
    aerich upgrade/downgrade

### Run code:

    fastapi dev